data.text:
Gather round the largest, most interactive picture frame in the house - your TV! With HP MediaSmart Connect you just select the Online Services menu to access your digital photos stored online at Snapfish. Show a slide show of photos from your most recent trip, a school recital, or birthday party to friends and family from the comfort of your couch.

See why more than 70 million Snapfish members worldwide love Snapfish by signing up for an account. Enjoy unlimited storage of photos and video clips in a safe and secure online location. Snapfish makes it easy to share your photos from vacations, weddings, baby's first year, and more. And itâs simple and quick to order prints and create unique gifts such as greeting cards, mugs, calendars, and more.

Print high-quality professionally-developed photos from wallet to wall size, it's easy with Snapfish. You can have your prints shipped to you or choose to pick them up at a participating store near you, all at an every-day low price.

Find photo gifts for all occasions in the Snapfish store. Create personalized greeting cards and custom photo books in styles and designs for every season and event. With over 100 personalized photo gifts to choose from, you'll find just what youâre looking for whether it's a greeting card, calendar, mug, photo book or mouse pad.

For more information and to sign up for an account, visit www.snapfish.com.
